程序包 com.tencent.tcr.sdk.api

接口 TcrErrorCode

  • public interface TcrErrorCode
    This interface defines common error codes of TcrSdk.

    • 字段概要

      字段 
      修饰符和类型 字段 说明
      static int ERR_INTERNAL_ERROR
      This indicates that some internal error has happened.
      static int ERR_INVALID_PARAMS
      This indicates that the request parameter is invalid.
      static int ERR_MULTIUSER_BASE_CODE
      The starting error code of the multiplayer module.
      static int ERR_STATE_ILLEGAL
      This indicates that the context state is illegal.
      static int ERR_TIMEOUT
      This indicates that the request is timed out.
      static int ERR_UNKNOWN
      This indicates that some unknown error has happened.
